    chunk_info ‚Üź (‚ČĘcnames)‚ćī‚äā‚ć¨
    chunks_rendered‚Üź0

    I‚Üź{‚ćļ[‚ćĶ]}
    Im‚Üź{‚ćļ[‚ćĶ;]}
    ‚ćĚ Chunk column index
    Ci ‚Üź cnames‚ąė‚ć≥‚ąė‚äÜ
    ‚ćĚ Chunk get
    ‚ćĚ Special cases:
    ‚ćĚ   - xz (zips x and z column)
    ‚ćĚ   - enc_xz (x z as decoded list -- note that isn't globally unique but is locally)
      Cg‚Üź{
          ‚ćĶ‚Č°'xz':‚Üď‚ćČ‚ÜĎchunk_info‚Ć∑‚ć®‚äāCi'cx' 'cz'
          ‚ćĶ‚Č°'enc_xz':(,‚ć®2*16)‚ä•‚ćČ‚äÉ,/‚ć™¬®chunk_info‚Ć∑‚ć®‚äāCi'cx' 'cz'
          chunk_info‚äÉ‚ć®Ci ‚ćĶ
