    mapi‚Üź(1500‚Ć∂)‚ć¨ ‚ćĚ (,‚ć®2*26)‚ä•x y
    empty_rle‚Üź(l‚čĄ(√ó/l‚čĄ)‚čĄ(0‚čĄ))

    ‚ąá Init(device save);vb_params;tb_params;p;cmd;pass;size;state;pxz
      vb_pools‚Üź{
          (cnt size)‚Üź‚ćĶ
          vb_params‚Üź##.SDL_GPU_BUFFERUSAGE_VERTEX size 0
          ({‚ćĶ,##.SDL_CreateGPUBuffer device vb_params}‚ć£cnt)‚ć¨
      }¬®‚Üď‚ćČ[vb_start_lens ‚čĄ 1‚Üďvb_sizes]
     
      tb_params‚Üź‚äā##.SDL_GPU_TRANSFERBUFFERUSAGE_UPLOAD(tb_size)0
      tb‚Üź##.SDL_CreateGPUTransferBuffer device tb_params
      'Error creating chunk transfer buffer'##.Assert tb
      ib‚Üź##.SDL_CreateGPUBuffer device(##.SDL_GPU_BUFFERUSAGE_INDEX isize 0)
     
      sam_params‚Üź‚äā0 0 0 2 2 2 0 4 0 0 200 1 0 0 0 0
      sampler‚Üź##.SDL_CreateGPUSampler device sam_params
      'Error creating chunk sampler'##.Assert sampler
      ‚ćĚ Do copy pass just to copy index buffer over
      ‚ćĚ Only need isize worth of indices by reasoning
      ‚ćĚ Overhead should be minimal if this is done once
      p‚Üź##.SDL_MapGPUTransferBuffer device tb 0
      _‚Üź##.LSE_MemcpyU32 p(indices)isize
      _‚Üź##.SDL_UnmapGPUTransferBuffer device tb
      cmd‚Üź##.SDL_AcquireGPUCommandBuffer device
      pass‚Üź##.SDL_BeginGPUCopyPass cmd
     
      _‚Üź##.SDL_UploadToGPUBuffer pass(tb 0)(ib 0 isize)0
      _‚Üź##.SDL_EndGPUCopyPass pass
      _‚Üź##.SDL_SubmitGPUCommandBuffer cmd
     
      seed‚Üźsave.‚éēVGET‚äā'seed' 42
      sns‚Üź(‚éēRL:seed)
      rand_vec‚Üź1 2‚óč‚ć§1‚äĘ‚ć™‚óč2√ósns.?256‚ćī0
      ptable‚Üź256 sns.?256
      :If ‚éēNEXISTS'saves/HelloWorld/map_data.dcf'
          map‚Üź'saves/HelloWorld/map_data.dcf'‚éēFSTIE 0
          mapi‚Üź(1500‚Ć∂)‚éēFREAD map 1
      :Else
          map‚Üź'saves/HelloWorld/map_data.dcf'(‚éēFCREATE‚ć†'Z' 1)0
          (1 3‚ćī0 ¬Į1 0)‚éēFSTAC map
          ‚ć¨ ‚éēFAPPEND map
      :EndIf
