    ‚ąá Release(device save)
      save.seed‚Üźseed
      {_‚Üź##.SDL_ReleaseGPUBuffer device ‚ćĶ}¬®‚ąävb_pools,(2‚Ć∑‚ćČvb_fenced),Cg'vb'
