    ‚ąá Queue_chunk(device blocks trans);x;z;vb
      (x z)‚Üźtrans
      chunk_info‚Üźchunk_info,¬®x,z,0‚ćī‚ć®¬Į2+‚ČĘcnames
      chunks‚ć™‚Üźblocks
