    ‚ąá info‚ÜźCopy_chunk(chunk ptr offset);flat;solid;edges;exposed;m;vert;tex;buf;vs;ic
      ‚ćĚ Collapse chunk @ x z and write it to ptr
      ‚ćĚ Return vertex size in bytes and number of indices
      ‚ćĚ IMPORTANT: Assumes that where data is being written to has enough space
      flat‚Üź‚ąächunk
      solid‚Üźchunk‚Č†0
      edges‚Üźsolid‚ąßbox
      ‚ćĚ (1) Returns format (16 32 16 3 2) where (3 2) are rotations
      ‚ćĚ (2) collapse into (vertex_num 6) multiply by index where not 0
      ‚ćĚ (3) index into box and 6wise multiply+‚ć≥add for texture index
      ‚ćĚ (4) index into texture and select exposed faces, duplicate 4 for faces
      ‚ćĚ (5) do some bitpacking here. Since we know x z ‚ąä [0, 16], they only take 5 bits
      ‚ćĚ     use the leading bit for uv coordinate into 4 corners (hence adding 128)
      ‚ćĚ     with this we only need 4 bytes for a vertex
      exposed‚Üź‚ÜĎ[0]{edges‚ą®solid>‚ćĶ}¬®0 1 2‚ąė.{‚ćĶ‚ĆĹ[‚ćļ]solid}¬Į1 1  ‚ćĚ (1)
      vert‚Üźvertices‚ĆŅ‚ć®4/m‚Üź‚ąäexposed
      tex‚Üź(‚ć≥√ó/l)(√ó‚ć§¬Į1),[1+‚ć≥2],[‚ć≥3]exposed                  ‚ćĚ (2)
      tex‚Üź‚ąä(‚ć≥6)(+‚ć§1)6√óflat[tex]                            ‚ćĚ (3)
      tex‚Üź4/m/,##.block_data.tex_z[tex]                    ‚ćĚ (4)
      vert+‚Üź(3,‚ć®‚ČĘvert)‚ćī128√ó[0 0 0 ‚čĄ 0 0 1 ‚čĄ 1 0 1 ‚čĄ 1 0 0] ‚ćĚ (5)
      buf‚Üź‚ąävert,tex
      vs‚Üź‚ČĘbuf
      ic‚Üź6√ó4√∑‚ć®‚ČĘvert
      _‚Üź##.LSE_MemcpyU8(ptr+offset)buf vs
      info‚Üźvs ic
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá Copy_chunks(device pass);m;p;vb;vi;vk;idxs;copied_info;dirty_m;null_m;vbs;xzs;sort
      :If 0=‚ČĘtb_queue
          :Return
      :EndIf
      tb_pos‚Üź0
     
      ‚ćĚ Copy into transfer buffer until full or queue is empty
      p‚Üź##.SDL_MapGPUTransferBuffer device tb 1
      idxs‚Üźtb_queue‚ć≥‚ć®Cg'xz'
      ‚ćĚ Copied info in total will be:
      ‚ćĚ.   (position into transfer buffer, vertex size, index count, vertex kind, vertex buffer)
      copied_info‚Üź{
          (vs ic)‚ÜźCopy_chunk(chunks‚Ć∑‚ć®idxs‚äÉ‚ć®‚ČĘ‚ćĶ ‚čĄ p ‚čĄ tb_pos)
          pos‚Üźtb_pos ‚čĄ tb_pos+‚Üźvs
          ‚ćĶ‚ć™(pos vs ic)
      }‚ć£{(tb_size‚Č§tb_pos+vsize)‚ą®‚ćļ‚Č•‚ć•‚ČĘidxs}‚äĘ0 3‚ćī0
      _‚Üź##.SDL_UnmapGPUTransferBuffer device tb
     
      ‚ćĚ Add vertex kinds (vb pool index)
      copied_info,‚Üźvb_sizes‚ąė‚ćł¬®1‚Ć∑‚ćČcopied_info
     
      idxs‚ÜĎ‚ć®‚Üź‚ČĘcopied_info
      m‚Üźidxs‚ąä‚ć®‚ć≥‚ČĘ‚äÉchunk_info
      ‚ćĚ Since queue and chunk)info are unsorted and might assign in a
      ‚ćĚ     different order, need to sort what has been selected from the
      ‚ćĚ     queue with what it's being assigned to
      sort‚Üź(‚äā‚ćč‚ćčm/Cg'xz')‚Ć∑‚ćčtb_queue‚ÜĎ‚ć®‚ČĘcopied_info
      copied_info‚Üź(‚äāsort)‚Ć∑copied_info
      tb_queue‚Üď‚ć®‚Üź‚ČĘcopied_info
     
      dirty_m‚Üźm‚ąß0‚Č†Cg'vb'
      vb_fenced‚ć™‚Üź¬Į1,'vb_kind'{‚ćČ‚ÜĎ‚ćļ ‚ćĶ}‚ć•{‚ćĶ/‚ć®dirty_m}‚ć•Cg'vb'
     
      vbs‚Üźdevice‚ąėFetch_buffer¬®3‚Ć∑‚ćČcopied_info
      copied_info,‚Üźvbs
     
      ‚ćĚ GPU Upload and set loaded chunks as ready with render info
      {(pos vs _ _ vb)‚Üź‚ćĶ ‚čĄ _‚Üź##.SDL_UploadToGPUBuffer pass(tb pos)(vb 0 vs)0}¬®‚Üďcopied_info
     
      (m/(Ci'idx_cnt')‚äÉchunk_info)‚Üź2‚Ć∑‚ćČcopied_info
      (m/(Ci'vb')‚äÉchunk_info)‚Üźvbs
      (m/(Ci'vb_kind')‚äÉchunk_info)‚Üź3‚Ć∑‚ćČcopied_info
      (m/(Ci'ready')‚äÉchunk_info)‚Üź1
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá Update_range(device x z);range;new;old;m;pair;blocks;c;t;set_m;ll;ax;az;dx;dz;surface;tr;ty;tz;ground;tx;idx;dirt;grass;p;grid;rns
      ll‚Üź2+2√óview_distance
      (ax az)‚Üź(‚Ćä16√∑‚ć®x z)
      (old_x old_z)‚Üź(ax az)
     
      range‚Üź(ax az ‚čĄ )+,‚ąė.,‚ć®(‚ć≥1+2√óview_distance)-view_distance
      ‚ćĚ Extra padding to account for bottom/right access
      ‚ćĚ Lattice is just [0, 256) since we index into gradient vectors
      lattice_range‚Üź(ax az ‚čĄ )+,‚ąė.,‚ć®(‚ć≥2+2√óview_distance)-view_distance-1
      lattice‚ÜźHash_byte seed,‚ÜĎlattice_range

      new‚Üźrange~Cg'xz'
      old‚Üźrange~‚ć®Cg'xz'
     
      ‚ćĚ Unload chunks
      m‚Üź~old‚ąä‚ć®Cg'xz' ‚ćĚ Kept
      { ‚ćĚ (major cell index ‚čĄ index into chunk hash array)
          (packR chunks‚Ć∑‚ć®‚äÉ‚ćĶ)‚éēFREPLACE(map ‚čĄ 2+1‚äÉ‚ćĶ)
      }{‚ćļ‚ćļ¬®‚ąė‚Üď‚ć£(~0‚ąä‚ćī‚ćĶ)‚äĘ‚ćĶ}(~m)‚ĆŅ‚ćČ[‚ć≥‚ČĘchunks ‚čĄ mapi‚ć≥Cg'enc_xz']
      chunks‚ĆŅ‚ć®‚Üźm
      ‚ćĚ chunks with vertex buffers write to fence buffer to be cycled back to pool
      set_m‚Üź(0‚Č†Cg'vb')‚ąß~m
      vb_fenced‚ć™‚Üź¬Į1,'vb_kind'{‚ćČ‚ÜĎ‚ćļ ‚ćĶ}‚ć•{‚ćĶ/‚ć®set_m}‚ć•Cg'vb'
      chunk_info‚Üźm‚ąė/¬®chunk_info
      ‚ćĚ rare case that chunk hasn't been given vertex buffer while being loaded
      ‚ćĚ (imagine on border of chunk strafing back and forth)
      tb_queue/‚ć®‚Üźtb_queue‚ąäCg'xz'
     
      ‚ćĚ access into the lattice grid
      ‚ćĚ https://www.scratchapixel.com/lessons/procedural-generation-virtual-worlds/procedural-patterns-noise-part-1/introduction.html
      ‚ćĚ https://www.scratchapixel.com/lessons/procedural-generation-virtual-worlds/perlin-noise-part-2/perlin-noise.html
      t‚Üź1(-,[0.5]‚äĘ)(16√∑‚ć®0.5+16 16‚ä§‚ć≥16*2)
      t‚Üźt√ót√ó(3-2√ót) ‚ćĚ Smoothstep
      t‚Üź2/,[2.5]t
     
      :For pair :In new
          idx‚Üź(,‚ć®2*16)‚ä•pair
          :If ~mapi‚ąä‚ć®idx
              mapi,‚Üźidx
              ‚ćĚ Total of 256 points (16*2) that are spread out on XZ chunks. 
              ‚ćĚ Twicefold Outer Product to get 4 points on the lattice each uses for bilinear interpolation
              ‚ćĚ For now hardcode terrain size (40+20√ó)
              c‚Üź256/‚ć™(,‚ć®view_distance)+pair-(ax az)
              idx‚Üź‚Ćä40+20√ó2√∑‚ć®+/+‚ĆŅ(‚ä£‚ĆŅt)√ó(‚äĘ‚ĆŅt)+‚ĆŅ‚ć§√ó‚ć§3‚äĘrand_vec Im lattice[(ll√ó‚ć≥2)‚ąė.+(‚ć≥2)‚ąė.+ll‚ä•c]
              blocks‚Üźl‚ćī1
     
              surface‚Üź‚Üď(16/‚ć≥16),(‚ć™idx),(256 1‚ćī‚ć≥16)
              blocks[surface-(0 2 0 ‚čĄ )]‚Üź0
              blocks‚Üź(#.block_data.Bi'Stone')@(1=‚äĘ)‚äĘ‚ąß‚ćÄ‚ć§2‚äĘblocks
              blocks[surface-(0 1 0 ‚čĄ )]‚Üź#.block_data.Bi'Dirt'
              blocks[surface-(0 2 0 ‚čĄ )]‚Üź#.block_data.Bi'Dirt'
              blocks[surface]‚Üź#.block_data.Bi'Grass'
     
              ‚ćĚ Tree :-)
              rns‚Üź(‚éēRL:|4192 4192 4192‚ä•pair,seed)
              (tx ground tz)‚Üź(0 ‚čĄ 1 ‚čĄ 0)+‚äÉsurface‚Ć∑‚ć®tree_spots‚äÉ‚ć®rns.?‚ČĘtree_spots
              ty‚Üź3+rns.?3
              blocks[tx;ground+‚ć≥ty;tz]‚Üź#.block_data.Bi'Log'
              blocks[tx+¬Į2+‚ć≥5;(ground ‚čĄ ground+1)+ty;tz+¬Į2+‚ć≥5]‚Üź#.block_data.Bi'Leaf'
              blocks[tx+¬Į1+‚ć≥3;(ground+2 ‚čĄ ground+3)+ty;tz+¬Į1+‚ć≥3]‚Üź#.block_data.Bi'Leaf'
              (packR blocks)‚éēFAPPEND map
          :Else
              blocks‚Üź0 packR ‚éēFREAD(map ‚čĄ 2+mapi‚ć≥idx)
          :EndIf
     
          Queue_chunk device blocks pair
      :EndFor
      mapi ‚éēFREPLACE(map ‚čĄ 1)
    ‚ąá


    ‚ąá Draw_chunks(cmd_buf pass px pz lx lz proj_view);w;m;vbs;inds;xz;ud;frs;n;d;box;h;t;t2;centers;extents;r
      ‚ćĚ Frustum Culling
      frs‚Üź##.player.Get_frustum(‚óč70√∑180 ‚čĄ 1280√∑720 ‚čĄ 0.1 ‚čĄ 500)
      n‚Üź3‚ÜĎ[1]frs
      d‚Üź,3‚Üď[1]frs
     
      ‚ćĚ https://web.archive.org/web/20220115111822/https://gdbooks.gitbooks.io/3dcollisions/content/Chapter2/static_aabb_plane.html
      centers‚Üź(w√∑2 ‚čĄ 2√∑‚ć®h‚Üź1‚äÉl ‚čĄ w√∑2)(+‚ć§1)‚ĆĹ2‚ĆĹ0,(w‚Üź‚äÉl)√ó‚ÜĎCg'xz'
      r‚Üź+/(|n)(√ó‚ć§1)(w ‚čĄ h ‚čĄ w)√∑2
      m‚Üź(Cg'ready')‚ąß‚ąß/(-r)(‚Č§‚ć§1)d(-‚ć§1)‚ć®n(+.√ó‚ć§2 1)centers
     
      chunks_rendered‚Üź+/m
      vbs‚Üźm/Cg'vb'
      inds‚Üźm/Cg'idx_cnt'
      ‚ćĚ Translation matrix for each chunk and rank-multiply to get MVPs for each
      ud‚Üź‚ąäproj_view(+.√ó‚ć§2)‚ć®‚äÉ‚ć™/{(x z)‚Üź‚ćĶ ‚čĄ ,[¬Į0.5](x 0 z 1)@3‚äĘ‚ąė.=‚ć®‚ć≥4}¬®(‚äÉl)√óm/Cg'xz'
      _‚Üź##.SDL_BindGPUFragmentSamplers pass 0(‚äā##.block_data.texture sampler)1
      _‚Üź##.SDL_BindGPUIndexBuffer pass(‚äāib 0)##.SDL_GPU_INDEXELEMENTSIZE_32BIT
      _‚Üź##.LSE_DrawListWithPushConstants cmd_buf pass vbs inds(‚ČĘvbs)ud 0 16
    ‚ąá

      Transform_points‚Üź{
          ‚ćĚ ‚ćĶ ‚Üź‚Üí vector of integers 3d space
          ‚ćĚ ‚ćļ ‚Üź‚Üí filter out invalid ones (default true)
          ‚ćĚ returns them in terms of locations into 4d chunk matrix
